## <a name="tech-stack">⚙️ Tech Stack</a>

<div align="center">

| Category | Technology | Purpose | Why We Chose It |
|----------|------------|---------|-----------------|
| **Framework** | React Native | Cross-platform mobile development | Native performance with code sharing |
| **Development Platform** | Expo SDK 50+ | Rapid development and deployment | Streamlined build process and OTA updates |
| **Language** | TypeScript | Type-safe development | Enhanced code quality and developer experience |
| **Styling** | NativeWind + Tailwind CSS | Utility-first styling system | Consistent, responsive design with minimal code |
| **Backend** | Appwrite | Backend-as-a-Service | Comprehensive backend solution with real-time features |
| **State Management** | Zustand | Global state management | Lightweight, performant, and easy to use |
| **Navigation** | Expo Router | File-based routing | Type-safe navigation with modern patterns |
| **Error Tracking** | Sentry | Error monitoring and performance | Production-ready error tracking and analytics |
| **Authentication** | Google OAuth + JWT | Secure user authentication | Industry-standard secure authentication |
| **Maps** | Google Maps API | Location services | Accurate delivery tracking and restaurant discovery |
| **Payments** | Stripe + PayPal | Payment processing | Secure, PCI-compliant payment handling |
| **Push Notifications** | Expo Notifications | Real-time user engagement | Native notification support across platforms |

</div>

### 🏗️ **Architecture Highlights**

```
📁 Project Structure
├── app/                    # Expo Router file-based routing
│   ├── (auth)/            # Authentication screens
│   ├── (tabs)/            # Main app navigation
│   └── modals/            # Modal screens and overlays
├── components/            # Reusable UI components
│   ├── ui/               # Base UI components
│   ├── forms/            # Form-specific components
│   └── layouts/          # Layout components
├── services/             # API calls and business logic
│   ├── api/              # Appwrite configuration
│   ├── auth/             # Authentication services
│   └── payments/         # Payment processing
├── stores/               # Zustand state management
├── types/                # TypeScript definitions
├── utils/                # Helper functions
└── constants/            # App constants and configuration
```

